--- statistical: range query on column with stats ---
  status:       applicable
  source:           statistical
  empirical_status: disabled
--- statistical: no stats, falls back to applicability_only ---
  status:       applicable
  source:           applicability_only
  empirical_status: disabled
--- default: empirical preferred over statistical when both available ---
  source:           empirical
  empirical_status: ok
--- unknown setting is rejected ---
UNKNOWN_SETTING
--- invalid value for empirical is rejected ---
INVALID_SETTING_VALUE
